# SmoothLookAt Function (3D)
#==================================================
#    SmoothLookAtRigid -> Call from integrate_forces()
#    SmoothLookAt for KinematicBody -> Call from _physics_process()
#    SmoothLookAt for Spatial/Node3D -> Call from _process()
#    ----------
#    nodeToTurn = the node you want to turn
#    targetPosition = the target position (Vector3) you want your nodeToTurn to face
#    turnSpeed = how long it will take nodeToTurn to face the direction you want it to face
#    ----------
#    -Z is assumed to be forward, the face/nose of your object
